About Us



Just imagine that…



You can communicate over the Internet with any native speaker as if they were sitting right in front of you understanding every word you say, and you, at the same time, fully understand what they are saying. There is no need for you to struggle to find the right words to say, “Hello” or ask about the other party’s health. No more wild gesticulations trying to convey your thoughts. During the video-meeting you will have an experienced interpreter, who will not only interpret the meaning of what you are saying to the other party but will also communicate your emotions and the context of the conversation through the language of another culture.



This is already possible today, and this is why we have created the Cloud Interpreter service. Cloud Interpreter is the first interpreter service in the world which is open 24/7 and is available directly from your browser.



Here are



five reasons



why you should definitely try our service:



1. Communicate freely



You will surely love the feeling of calm and confidence communicating with a foreign partner which the support of a professional interpreter will provide. We give you the luxury of free communication, unencumbered with formalities. Concentrate on what is important for you—we will make sure that you are properly understood.



2. Price



From now on you won’t need to spend money on a trip abroad to conduct negotiations, discuss the progress of a project or consult a doctor or a lawyer. No more overhead expenses: you pay only for the amount of interpreting you need. A minimal order is a 15-minutes’ interpreting. The length of the video-meetings is unlimited.



3. Time



Your partner will see and hear you at any time and place convenient for both of you. Take your tablet or smartphone with you while travelling—and you can hold a conversation from any place provided with an Internet connection: sitting in a café, staying at a hotel or even lying on a beach! No more time spent on complicated arrangements, booking hotels or long flights. Placing an order on our web-site will only take a few minutes.



4. Distance



Our service is available from any part of the globe where there is a reliable high-speed Internet connection. Distance won’t matter anymore. Do you need to have a video-talk with someone from Australia or Argentina? A piece of cake! The only thing you should keep in mind is the time difference; but we have taken care of this as well: when ordering our service you may choose the time for your conversation that is suitable both for you and for your partner.



5. Technologies



Our service takes advantage of the great potential of present-day technologies available to everyone. You will see that your PC, tablet or smartphone can work for you in a much more effective way and can save much more of your time and money. We guarantee the support for modern mobile devices and we are constantly working on extending the list of supporting browsers.



